en made profits from their sites with high-quality contents, cooperation with companies or ads."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Some of blog owners"}]},{"type":"text","value":", however, styled their blogs with tons of animations, colors and weird shapes, impressing the viewers most of whom were just new to this fancy world."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"…"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A blog is one’s free zone."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It was 2010. At my age of 12, with the desire to have my own “free zone”, I stepped onto the road to seek my dream blog."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2010-2013: Exploration"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"lofter, QQZone…"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Several blog services from online providers are full of functions out of box and have no hassles to use them, but always left me unsatisfied: they make me feel "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"limited"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"WordPress, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://typecho.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"typecho"}]},{"type":"text","value":"…"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When I started to learn the skills to build a site,  I found self-hosting blog fancier and more attractive. I chose "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"typecho"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for its simplicity and customizability. The joy, proud and satisfaction when I applied a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Windows 8 Metro"}]},{"type":"text","value":" theme onto my "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-text"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"typecho"}]},{"type":"text","value":" site hosted on "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://sae.sina.com.cn/?m=dashboard"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAE"}]},{"type":"text","value":" in 2012 are still fresh and rememberable today."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"My days in junior high school were complemented by the exploration of and the attempts to crafting the best blog for myself."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2013: Dimmed Spark"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The story doesn’t end here. Despite of the rich functionalities and customizability, these blogs are still programmed by others. The "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"limits"}]},{"type":"text","value":" still exist."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As I grew up and learned more, I started to seek for "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"something truly mine, something that I am the true master of"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It was a hot day in my summer vacation, after the High School Entrance Exam. A seemingly crazy idea struke me."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How about building my blog by myself from scratch?"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I could implement WHATEVER functions I WANT, decorated my blog with WHATEVER I WANT, and kept up with the rapidly developing technical trend. In other words, I will never be "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LIMITED"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"During the development, my techniques can be trained, making me a better programmer."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Implementing my own’s blog is "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SO COOOOOOOOL"}]},{"type":"text","value":" anyway, isn’t it?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"But it is impossible."}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I was only slightly capable of writing simple programs with VBS and C#."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"HTML/CSS were aliens to me, not to mention full-fledge programming languages and framework."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What’s worse, high school was around the corner. If I would like to be admitted into a good university, I had to focus on study more than anything else. Not only self-building blog but the all the blog things must be compromised."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It was 2013."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Building my own personal blog was an idea emerged at my age of 15…"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"which was put aside."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2016-Now:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"To be continued…"}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"Preface","slug":"preface"},{"depth":2,"value":"Pre-2010: Awareness","slug":"pre-2010-awareness"},{"depth":1,"value":"2010-2013: Exploration","slug":"2010-2013-exploration"},{"depth":1,"value":"2013: Dimmed Spark","slug":"2013-dimmed-spark"},{"depth":1,"value":"2016-Now:","slug":"2016-now"}]}}}